lyrics.stanza:
Jehovah bless you and keep you;
Jehovah make His face shine upon you
And be gracious to you;
Jehovah lift up His countenance upon you
And give you peace.

God the Father's keeping;
God the Son is shining;
God the Spirit's countenance
Cheering, uplifting you;
What a Triune blessing;
God Himself dispensing,
For your rich enjoyment
All your days.
